{"tid":535510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬拉松賽多名跑手不適有一名男子昏迷送院","createTime":"2018-01-21T03:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T04:58:18.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0e883c103b89a175e1aca2dd910bd6336c7608d7","tid":535510,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:11:19.000Z","msg":"香港馬拉松早上舉行，全馬比賽在早上六時十分左右起步，由行政長官林鄭月娥和警務處長盧偉聰主持起步禮。不少跑手都說，今日天氣較為濕，會小心調節呼吸，希望盡力跑完全程。但比賽期間有多名跑手跌倒或抽筋不適，要即場接受治理，有一名男跑手送院時昏迷。<br />\n<br />\n十公里賽男女子壯年組冠軍由本港三項鐵人賽選手包辦，其中第五年參賽，二十一歲的鄭汝鏗在男子組奪冠後說，對首名衝線感意外，亦創造了自己最佳時間。至於女子組冠軍蔡欣妍，第四年參賽，她對奪冠感到興奮，認為自己對賽事有經驗，體能和策略上都有進步。而十公里輪椅挑戰賽，冠軍是首次參賽的李豪飛。半馬比賽由內地跑手李春暉及郝曉帆包辦男女子組冠軍。"},{"pid":"d3366c6719ad0aaf255154ef405d76a43a756eb0","tid":535510,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:12:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe6c154886a1f2e97b43e2fba7480fad2c430687","tid":535510,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516499405_d508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180121%2Flarge%2F1516499405_d508.jpg&h=916137d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516497192_baee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180121%2Flarge%2F1516497192_baee.jpg&h=ffed88b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516502264_4587.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180121%2Flarge%2F1516502264_4587.jpg&h=58b60502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516502265_deed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsta